# RTL & Urdu

`lang="ur" dir="rtl"` · logical spacing (`ms/me/ps/pe`) · `leading-[1.8]`+ · `rtl:rotate-180` on directional icons

**Urdu required** for all user-visible text. Run `npm run check:urdu`. False positive: `// urdu-ok`

Full allow/deny list: `CLAUDE.md` § Urdu-First Frontend Rule.

`prefers-reduced-motion` in `Reveal` / `globals.css`.
